gnal that a generic error should be reported.\n\nThe provided expression does not contain expression metavariables or `sorry`, but\nlevel metavariables may be present. We assume these do not affect evaluation.\nIf `expectedType?` is provided, then the expression is coerced as necessary to have this type.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/ConfigEval/Types.html#Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr.evalExpr","kind":"def","line":66,"name":"Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr.evalExpr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/ConfigEval/Types.lean#L66-L66"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/ConfigEval/Types.html#Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">ConfigEval</span>.<span class=\"name\">EvalExpr</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>} → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">Lean.MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/ConfigEval/Types.html#Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr\">Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/ConfigEval/Types.html#Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr.mk","kind":"ctor","line":53,"name":"Lean.Elab.ConfigEval.EvalExpr.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lea